                  </hi>. I received the order from the last witness—I packed up the bales described in the order, and found the tickets upon them—these were marked <hi rend="italic">Jacomb and Son's Sale lot</hi> 717 <hi rend="italic">A. M.</hi> (2, 3, 4)—I issued a pass for them, and delivered them into a van.</p>
